data.description: SELLER WILL CONTRIBUTE $10,000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COST OR INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN!  Turn Key and Ready to be called Home!  Welcome to this charming, renovated 4BR/2BA home on a spacious quarter-acre lot! Centrally located in Wellswood, this house has it all. The kitchen boasts an island, granite countertops, and stainless-steel appliances. The fenced backyard features a screened lanai with a built-in wet bar, perfect for entertaining. New AC Ducks with blown in insulation throughout.  Plus, there are 2 sheds for extra storage. With its convenient location near 275, you can easily reach downtown Tampa or the airport in just 15 minutes. Don't miss out on this dream home! Schedule your showing today!
